We are not taking anymore resume for this opening. Thank you.   BAT Bangladesh is looking for two individuals for (1) Global Graduate - LEX (Legal &  External Affairs) (Circular in the comment) and (2) Global Graduate - Human Resources.   Anyone interested is requested to drop their resume at s.rimen78@gmail.com. kindly mention in the comment if you have anyone in mind too. Thank you!

post_description: 'Battle of Minds', is one of the most eminent idea-based competition hosted by BAT Bangladesh, is coming to the Bangladesh Agricultural University to conduct a roadshow. post_description: Mohammad Rafique was the first Bangladeshi bowler to take 100 Test wickets during his last international match. He played 159 international matches for the Tigers across three formats and scalped 226 wickets. Rafique was instrumental with the bat as well who became the first Bangladeshi batsman to hit a Test century batting at number 9 against West Indies at St. Lucia in 2004.   #KnowYourHerors
